    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、フェスに向けての作業の\n進捗報告をまとめたので目を通していただけますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I've compiled a progress report on our work\nfor the festival. Could you please take a look?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6366.666682600001,
          "startTime": 8.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、みんなには企画の立案だけじゃなく\n細かい作業まで手伝ってもらってすまないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ and I'm sorry everyone helped not only with planning\nbut also with the small details",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7693885963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで下さい\nみんな好きでやってることですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't mind\nWe all do this because we love it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "一丸になって、楽しんで物事に取り組む……\n私達は星見プロのそういうところが好きなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Working together and have fun…\nThat's what we like about Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.5783450922
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……星見プロには、みんなで作り上げるという\n文化が根付いているのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Maybe Hoshimi Prods. has a culture of\ncreating things together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "今回はステージショー、展示企画、グッズ製作等で\nグループ分けして、分担作業を行っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time‚ we are working in groups‚ dividing into\nstage shows‚ exhibition planning‚ and goods production",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.1321545125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、会場内のイートインで提供する\nコラボメニューの考案を遙子さんと葵さんが担当……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For example‚ Haruko-san and Aoi-san are in charge of designing\nthe collaboration menu to be served at the venue's eat-in…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "物販で売るオリジナルTシャツの製作を\n千紗とfranさんが担当……といった具合です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa and fran-san are in charge of creating the original T-shirts\nto be sold as goods… That's the current status",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.2616558235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "franさんも手伝ってくれるのか？\nこういうことにはあまり乗り気じゃないと思っていたが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is fran-san helping us too?\nShe didn't want to get involved in this kind of thing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 64.8575286089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "そこは、グッズの製作会社と売上の5～10パーで\nどうかと交渉して、やる気になったみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think she was motivated to do it because she somehow negotiated\na 5-10% share of sales with the goods manufacturer",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.5658731939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみにkanaさんはSNSでバズりそうだから\nmihoさんは試したい演出があるから手伝うそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ kana-san said she thinks it'll be popular on SNS‚\nmiho-san said she'd like to try out a skill and offer to help",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "損得勘定で考えて、自分達に利益があるから手伝うのか\nそういうところはちゃっかりしているな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are they helping out because they think it will benefit them?\nThat's a clever thing to do",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.2909067316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "協力してもらえるのは心強いですが\n千紗がfranさんとうまくやれるか少し心配です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's reassuring to have their cooperation‚\nbut I'm a little worried about whether Chisa will get along with fran-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "二人は性格が全然違うからな……\n心配なら、沙季が千紗をサポートしたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They have completely different personalities…\nIf you're worried‚ why don't you support Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.0112471107
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "私もそう思って、二人の打ち合わせに付き添って\n試しに服のデザインを提案してみたのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought the same‚ so I accompanied them to their meeting\nand tried out some clothing designs‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "「ここは私達に任せてお姉ちゃんは他の人を手伝って\nあげて」と千紗にやんわり追い出されてしまい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa gently kicked me out and saying‚ 'Leave this\nto us and help out the others'…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.9402038419
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "千紗がどんどん自立していくようで……お姉ちゃんと\nしては頼もしいやら寂しいやら、複雑な心境です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa seems to be becoming more and more independent… I have mixed feelings\nas an one-san‚ feeling both reassured and lonely",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……それ、追い出されたのは\n別の理由のような気もするな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's‚ maybe there's\nanother reason you were kicked out",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.1935485527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 134.9644215588
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
