    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのアイドルをモチーフにした\nコラボメニューの試作品がようやく完成したわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The prototype for the collaboration menu\nfeaturing Hoshimi Production idols is finally complete",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子が作ったランチ二種類に\n僕が作ったデザート二種類……早速試食してみようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko made two lunches‚\nand I made two desserts… Let's try it quickly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "は？　何さっさと食べようとしてんの？\n写真を撮らずに食べ始めるなんてあり得ないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Why are you trying to eat so quickly?\nI don't understand why you wouldn't take a picture of it and eat",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
