      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで\nどうしてkanaがここにいるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…By the way‚\nwhy is kana here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "あんた達だけじゃメニュー作りも進まないだろうし\nkanaがわざわざ手伝いに来てやったんでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You guys wouldn't have been able to make much progress on the menu by yourself\nkana came all the way here to help out",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
